info.name: Userlist Icons
info.description:
A fun way to jazz up your userlist, installing this will allow you to see not only your own but others userlist icons! ( If you would like yours visible to others using this stylish post here: http://www.smogon.com/forums/threads/userlist-icons-stylish.3551505/ )

THIS STYLISH IS COMPATIBLE WITH ALL OTHER USERSTYLES ETC.
